    "from_id": "1000000001",
    "message_id": "1000000",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Can you grab Kenji on Tuesday? I have a 3:30 at the Kirkland office and there's no way I'm back in Bellevue by 2:45 pickup."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000001",
    "date": "1766687400",
    "from_id": "1000000002",
    "message_id": "1000001",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Yeah I can do it. Taiko's not until 7 so I've got the window. He gets out at 2:45?"
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000001",
    "date": "1766687400",
    "from_id": "1000000001",
    "message_id": "1000002",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "2:45 yeah. Also he keeps asking if he can come watch your class sometime 😂"
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000001",
    "date": "1766687400",
    "from_id": "1000000002",
    "message_id": "1000003",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Tell him it's beginner level. I'm the slowest person in the room most weeks. Gambatte is aimed at me, not the eight-year-olds."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000001",
    "date": "1766687400",
    "from_id": "1000000001",
    "message_id": "1000004",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "He genuinely does not care. His logic is: dad + drums = automatically cool. You're overthinking it."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000001",
    "date": "1766687400",
    "from_id": "1000000002",
    "message_id": "1000005",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Can't argue with that math. I'll grab him Tuesday, we'll stop at Uwajimaya on the way home. See you after class, probably 9ish."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000002",
    "date": "1766601000",
    "from_id": "1000000001",
    "message_id": "1000006",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Dad how was taiko last night 🥁 did you mess up the ending again lol"
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000002",
    "date": "1766601000",
    "from_id": "1000000003",
    "message_id": "1000007",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "I did not mess up the ending. I was slightly behind the beat. Different thing."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000002",
    "date": "1766601000",
    "from_id": "1000000001",
    "message_id": "1000008",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "that is literally the same thing 😭"
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000002",
    "date": "1766601000",
    "from_id": "1000000003",
    "message_id": "1000009",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Sensei said I improved. That's the official record. Don't push it."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000002",
    "date": "1766601000",
    "from_id": "1000000001",
    "message_id": "1000010",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "you're so competitive about *beginner* taiko. you land 737s for a living and this is what gets you"
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000002",
    "date": "1766601000",
    "from_id": "1000000003",
    "message_id": "1000011",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Gambatte applies everywhere. Be outside at 3, I'm picking you up today."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000003",
    "date": "1766514600",
    "from_id": "1000000001",
    "message_id": "1000012",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Taiko's tomorrow at 7 — the dojo has observer spots if you want to come. Yoshiko keeps saying you'd get into it and honestly she's probably right."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000003",
    "date": "1766514600",
    "from_id": "1000000004",
    "message_id": "1000013",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "wait the beginner class you've been going to? how long does it run"
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000003",
    "date": "1766514600",
    "from_id": "1000000001",
    "message_id": "1000014",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "One hour. I'm still nowhere near good but the fundamentals are clicking. Worth seeing at least once."
  },
